rComments: Despite the negative reviews, he was a very good teacher and cared about how his students did and made an effort to learn some names. His style of teaching is to uses simple power point slides as an aid to his lecture and do chalk board examples on the board. He taught concepts, and was very interesting to listen to during lectures.

He is an incredibly terrible teacher, and what's worse is that he doesn't know how to test people based on what he "teaches". Unbelievable. He should just put his focus on his research and quit teaching.

Worst professor at the university. Cannot teach. Useless material. Gives all problems to TA's. Midterms cover nothing from class. Labs are useless. Expectations Unclear. Disrespectful of all students and the University Constitution.

Unreasonable, unclear. His ppt slides are completely useless. Very disrespectful. Not helpful.
